questiontext.text: Please place the markers on the map of Milton Keynes and be aware that there is more than one railway station.

generalfeedback.text: The Open University is at the junction of Brickhill Street and Groveway. There are three railway stations, Wolverton, Milton Keynes Central and Bletchley.

hint.text: You should be looking to place four markers on the map.
You should be looking to place markers on three railway stations.
